plot: On their last day in Palm Springs, Gina, Emily, and Shannon are busy trying to untangle Elizabeth's ever-changing stories, while Kelly warns Elizabeth that the ladies are on to her. Back in the OC, Coronavirus starts to infiltrate their world causing Shannon to go into full panic mode. Kelly fears for her business, Gina deals with personal matters, and Emily worries about school closures. In therapy, Braunwyn works through her past issues that led her to sobriety and becomes increasingly anxious about staying sober as the impending lockdown looms.—Anonymous
